events.description:
"Music of the Soul" 
J.S. Bach: Cantata: "Mein Herze schwimmt im Blut," BWV 199; 
Mozart: Concert Aria: "Misera, Dove son!...Ah! non son'io che parlo," K. 369; 
Bruckner: Symphony No. 4 in E-flat Major, "Romantic".

Harry Davidson is celebrating his 25th season as music director of the Duke Symphony Orchestra. Admission is free. 

Siyeon Kim is a Doctor of Musical Arts (DMA) student in Voice Performance at the University of Iowa. She received her MM in Voice/Opera Performance at the Manhattan School of Music, and an Artist Diploma in Voice at the Cleveland Institute of Music.
